{"title":"草地行","authors":["简五一"],"dates":[{"year":1996,"month":10,"day":14}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"草地行"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"简五一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"莽莽荒原，在晨曦里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闪烁着无数晶莹的珍珠。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每株野草拥着一轮太阳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在翠色叶片上，肃然起舞。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拂晓。草地刚走过一标人马，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"硝烟弹痕，鞭打着古铜色的肌肤。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人马在泥淖里疲惫地跋涉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"步伐却坚决地犁开漫天黑雾……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"倒下的，甘心与荒原融为一体；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走着的，永远铺展希望的坦途。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红的旗帜和铁的刀枪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"灼烤的草地滚烫、火红！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"于是，当地火终"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"于染透晨曦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"霞光中矗立着信"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"念的雕塑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"于是，草地就托"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"起千万轮太阳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为革命和未来虔"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"诚的祝福"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}